HEADWORD: Deep-waisted
<hw>Deep"-waist`ed</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <fld>(Naut.)</fld>
<def>Having a deep waist, as when, in a ship, the poop and forecastle
are much elevated above the deck.</def>⟦br⟧
